For example, to process the following response, you would use /results for the result
			field
			path:{  
   "count":"1023",
   "startAt":"2",
   "maxResults":"2",
   "total":"6",
   "results":[  
      {  
         "firstName":"Joe",
         "lastName":"Smith",
         "phone":"555-555-5555"
      },
      {  
         "firstName":"Jimmy",
         "lastName":"Smott",
         "phone":"333-333-3333"
      },
      {  
         "firstName":"Joanne",
         "lastName":"Smythe",
         "phone":"777-777-7777"
      }
   ]
}

From this data, the origin creates three records. The first
			record:{  
   "firstName":"Joe",
   "lastName":"Smith",
   "phone":"555-555-5555"
}
